    <section id="today">
      <h2>Play with the page</h2>
      <p>
        Use the timeline to load moments into the ‚Äúscreen.‚Äù Or press the three buttons:
        <span class="kbd">A</span> cycles moods, <span class="kbd">B</span> gives snacks (confetti!), and <span class="kbd">C</span> jumps to the next timeline event.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>A:</strong> changes screen mode (History / Trivia / Vibes)</li>
        <li><strong>B:</strong> snack time (pet gets happier)</li>
        <li><strong>C:</strong> next event (like scrolling time)</li>
      </ul>
